channel.title: Delete 2nd story walls and roofs
channel.description:
Hello all, I am attempting to remove the walls and roof from edge bank on my server. I've managed to delete everything on the first story but i cant figure out how to remove second story walls and the roof. been trying different object IDs and nothing is working. any ideas?
[IMG]http://i60.tinypic.com/4dp55.png[/img]

item.title: Delete 2nd story walls and roofs
item.dc:creator: @matzie matzie
item.description:
@matzie wrote:

I am not sure that a default server has support for this. The only thing i could guess is use (11-20) instead of 10 for the object type.

I think you are better off using a cache editor and deleting it in there, it will save you from the server spam on connect every time as well.

Read full topic
